Package: photonicat-pm-dkms
Architecture: all
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
Description: dkms sources for photonicat-pm power manager driver
 This package provides the dkms source code for the photonicat-pm
 power manager driver. It handles battery status, charger monitoring,
 RTC, hardware monitoring, thermal fan control, motion detection,
 status LED/beeper control, network status LED, PMU version reporting,
 power-on event tracking, and power/reboot management.
